    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1867-03-09T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1867-03-09T00:00:00-05:00" n="466"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d466">
                <head>
                    <persName type="from">Mr. Seward</persName> to <persName type="to">Mr.
                        Hovey</persName>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 45.]</seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>, <hi rend="italic"
                                >Washington</hi>,</placeName>
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1867-03-09">
                            <hi rend="italic">March</hi> 9, 1867</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir :</hi> Pursuant to the last paragraph of the enclosure
                    (despatch No. 59, to Mr. Hale) contained in my despatch to you, No. 44, of
                    yesterday, I transmit herewith a copy of two notes<note n="*" xml:id="d466fn1"
                        >For enclosures see despatches from United States minister to Chili and
                        Ecuador dated February 2, 1867, and numbered respectively 39 and 25.</note>
                    which the ministers of foreign affairs of Chili and Ecuador respectivelly
                    addressed to the minister of the United States in their country in reply to his
                    note, transmitting a copy of the propositions contained in our offer of
                    mediation which is embodied in the despatch to you, No. 36, of the 20th of last
                    December.</p>
                <p>I am, sir, your obedient servant,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>WILLIAM H. SEWARD.</signed>
                </closer>
                <postscript>
                    <p>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Alvin P. Hovey</hi>, Esq., <hi rend="italic">&amp;c.,
                            &amp;c., &amp;c.</hi>
                    </p>
                </postscript>
            </div>
        </body>
